item.title: Profile
item.description: Biography Link to heading I am an Assistant Professor in the Department of Computer Science at Aalborg University. I am a faculty member in Center for Data-Intensive Systems. I am also affiliated with the department’s team on Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning and the university’s Center on AI for the People. I obtained my Ph.D. degree in Computer Science at Aalborg University in April 2021 under the supervision of Prof.
